# Apply for production credentials 

Learn how to apply for production credentials for CTC Traders API.

## Submitting your readiness checklist for existing and new software

When you are confident that your software is fully compatible with NCTS6 or if you already have production access to
NCTS5/CTC Traders v2.1, then you will need to submit your readiness checklist:

- Fill in and tick all the sections of the [NCTS6 Readiness Checklist.docx form (Microsoft Word document)](/guides/ctc-traders-testing-guide/downloads/NCTS6_Readiness_Checklist_1.0_07_04_26.docx)
  - You only need to provide evidence of a completed outbound transit movement (IE015 to IE029) for production access testing
- You must sign and date the checklist
- When ready, log into your developer hub account and email your completed form here: **[Support Form](https://eur03.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.service.hmrc.gov.uk%2Fdevhub-support%2Fstart&data=05%7C02%7Csamir.luqman%40hmrc.gov.uk%7Cca83aeece88d482de89808de6e2a7b7f%7Cac52f73cfd1a4a9a8e7a4a248f3139e1%7C0%7C0%7C639069325927157465%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&sdata=eFauVbA9AlpbrFcp6fob7X1AHtgOMHkn7l5tjJhHT9s%3D&reserved=0)**
- We will check your test evidence using the information you provided in the form
- When we are satisfied that you have completed a sufficient level of testing, you will be granted access to the live API system but this access can be used only after the UK NCTS6 service goes live

**Important**: Any test results submitted with production credentials applications must be less than 14 days old.